{"tid":2152473,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"初創公司盼可用「香港設計」　商界：中國製造非不值錢","createTime":"2020-08-12T04:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T04:20:44.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f975a7b8ad3de6d7bd349d7b396bf2a0395b1257","tid":2152473,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T04:15:11.000Z","msg":"有本港初創公司希望本港當局能爭取能沿用「香港製造」標籤，否則會考慮日後在產品上標示為「香港設計」。<br />\n<br />\n有本港商會表示，雖然香港製造較吃香，但中國製造並非不值錢，認為美方做法是政治原因大於一切。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543265-20200812.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543265-20200812.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=a616b37f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543265-20200812.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b7ee091f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543265-20200812.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6802cc505d81358dbfddbc6f1d3823b63288e3aa","tid":2152473,"uid":89641,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T04:16:20.000Z","msg":"你問下全世界包括非洲, 一件野MADE IN CHINA定MADE IN VIETNAM值錢D?"},{"pid":"98db783f18b59bc9ff82610db72bcbc235e6fad9","tid":2152473,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T04:16:20.000Z","msg":"一個中國咁又唔得, follow 支共講法又係政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a29a98f73a2f87a6dcb1287c9e0fd37e407756","tid":2152473,"uid":18411,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T04:17:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">雖然香港製造較吃香，但中國製造並非不值錢</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmo